{"tid":38393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被判抄襲停售 Apple怒告北京知識產權局","createTime":"2016-12-14T01:48:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T05:05:24.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26b03f0807b3329f24b2d279a5f4ea4cac884a5a","tid":38393,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:48:37.000Z","msg":"還記得今年6月份這個轟動全球的新聞嗎？iPhone 6／6 Plus被一間不知名的中國公司－佰利Baili控告，說是侵犯了旗下一款名為100C的手機專利。而最讓人嚇到的是，這間中國公司竟然贏了這起官司，北京知識產權局宣判：兩個手機 &ldquo;無明顯差異&rdquo;，iPhone 6／6 Plus禁止在中國北京售賣！！<br />\n<br />\n目前，Apple以違反程序、越權為由，竟然將北京知識產權局告上法院！為北京知識產權法院也受理了這起案件，在過去的12月7日開庭審訊！<br />\n<br />\n由於佰利公司今次不是被告，所以他們只以第三證人方式出庭應訊。<br />\n<br />\n有備而來的Apple律師團表示，主要訴求為：<br />\n<br />\n撤銷北京知產局的《專利侵權糾紛處理決定書》<br />\n<br />\n宣判 iPhone6、iPhone6 Plus未侵犯佰利公司的外觀專利權！<br />\n<br />\n進行激烈辯論後，法庭將擇期宣判此案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/technology/player?newsId=203592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203592&d=Mh6jipTtZVbNO3LhJl7X4GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=68163190\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Ftechnology%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203592&h=0f117471\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/technology/player?newsId=203592</a>"},{"pid":"c16847cccab231414d56070018df72304e48dac4","tid":38393,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:50:57.000Z","msg":"輸硬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eacf19b444785d2bbe6af787aa12925e70e3110","tid":38393,"uid":8229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"同個強姦犯戴套先強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9742aac874cbfa42380006eff0752c56c10626ac","tid":38393,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"中國冇得賣iPhone,先達佬最開心"},{"pid":"15a99e3daa32db9fe6fdde97ca4a4ba9454d2fa8",